Class BatchedPaxosPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.nio.JSONPacket
      • edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.paxospackets.PaxosPacket
        • edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.paxospackets.BatchedPaxosPacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Summarizable

    public class BatchedPaxosPacket
extends PaxosPacket
    Author:
    arun A general-purpose batched paxos packet. This is useful to extract batching benefits even with many groups just by batching together paxos packets destined to the same set of destinations. We might as well try to extract blood out of stone.
